  <summary date="2021-06-29T17:07:04Z" status="Introduced in House">Securing Access for Venue Equity Act or the SAVE Act

This bill expands a grant program established to support venue operators in response to COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) to include hospitality businesses, such as amusement and theme parks, scenic and sightseeing transportation businesses, and travel arrangement and reservation services.</summary>
